bgDescription: Originally a dish invented by Huanglong miners who were too busy to cook, Maocai is prepared simply by mixing and stewing all ingredients with spices in one pot.
description: Increases all team members' Crit. Rate by 28%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
